  "title": "Recruitment Consultant",
  "description": "<p>Job Description:</p><ul><li>Manage full recruitment process including sourcing for candidates, posting job advertisements, interviewing, profiling, and talent management</li><li>Develop and cultivate strong working relationships with clients, candidates & other collaborators</li><li>Place candidates out to clients to assist in their staffing requirements</li><li>Manage job offer closure and salary negotiation process</li><li>Work closely with clients for business development and account management</li></ul><p>What we are looking for:</p><ul><li>Diploma/Degree in any discipline</li><li>A team player who enjoys interacting with people, sales-driven and works well in a fast-paced environment</li><li>Excellent communication & interpersonal skills</li></ul><p><br /><strong>How to Apply</strong></p><p>Send your updated CV to <a href=\"mailto:deborah@crew.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>deborah@crew.sg</strong></a> with:</p><ul><li><p>Your expected salary</p></li><li><p>Last drawn package</p></li><li><p>Notice period / earliest start date</p></li></ul><p>Only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p><p><br /><strong>Ho Yu Qing Deborah (R1104551)</strong><br />CREW by HRnet | HRnet Ventures Pte Ltd<br />EA Licence: <strong>24C2435</strong></p>",
